st: the third sunday in lent
tb: Heavenly Father, you have made us for yourself, and our hearts are restless until they rest in
    you: Look with compassion upon the heartfelt desires of your servants, and purify our
    disordered affections, that we may behold your eternal glory in the face of Christ Jesus; who
    lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit, one God, for ever and ever. **Amen.**
